rx.subscriptions

Class SerialSubscription

  • java.lang.Object
    • rx.subscriptions.SerialSubscription
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Subscription

    public final class SerialSubscription
extends java.lang.Object
implements Subscription
    Represents a subscription whose underlying subscription can be swapped for another subscription which causes the previous underlying subscription to be unsubscribed.
    See Also:
    Rx.Net equivalent SerialDisposable

      • unsubscribe

        public void unsubscribe()
        Description copied from interface: Subscription
        Stop receiving notifications on the Subscriber that was registered when this Subscription was received.

        This allows unregistering an Subscriber before it has finished receiving all events (ie. before onCompleted is called).

        Specified by:
